    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/89a98051355ee37c9dc5ca3f77fe02f3.avif?t=1770163053\" width=800 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/b7a4cbbf12b03a50d64d426910734de2.avif?t=1770163053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras_big/b7a4cbbf12b03a50d64d426910734de2.avif?t=1770163053 width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in ANGEL, a narrative driven racing adventure, where digital climate change threatens the <strong>eCho</strong> network with extinction. As eCho faces its extinction, the ANGEL protocol - <strong>EXPLORE, CREATE, REFLECT</strong>- persists. Embark on a journey that questions what it means to be connected. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>Alpha-Demo</strong> players are granted access to the <strong>first two worlds</strong> of the opening story mode, averaging roughly 1-2 hours of gameplay. You will connect to the eCho network, develop your input capabilities with new combos and abilities, and learn how the game is structured. This Alpha-Demo is an opportunity to provide direct feedback to me (the developer) so that I can make the best possible full release. All reviews and feedback are encouraged!<br><br>ANGEL imbues the flow state of racing with the complexity of breakbeat music enhanced by a soundtrack from MyraTV, and many other breakbeat enthusiasts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/51e5f6a032a11e0c0b182aa4c10bdbe6.poster.avif?t=1770163053\" width=646 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/51e5f6a032a11e0c0b182aa4c10bdbe6.webm?t=1770163053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/51e5f6a032a11e0c0b182aa4c10bdbe6.mp4?t=1770163053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
